The Annex to Regulation (EC) No 678/2002 is corrected as follows:
1. in the column "Product code", the code " 0805 30 10 91/00 " is replaced by the code " 0805 50 10 91/00 ";
2. in the column "Destination", in the line corresponding to product codes " 0808 10 20 91/00, 0808 10 50 91/00 and 0808 10 90 91/00 ", the destination codes "F04 and F09" are replaced by the code "F09".
